ADB (Android Debug Bridge)
--------------------------
adb connect <target_ip_address>
adb disconnect
adb shell
adb install <appName.apk>
adb uninstall <package_name>
adb push <file_name> <destination_path>
adb pull <file_name>
adb logcat

apktool
-------
apktool d <apk_name.apk> //for decompiling
apktool b <folder> -o <new_apk_name.apk> //for rebuilding
